  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced chorizo and cook until browned, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the smoked chicken broth, bring to a boil, and then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the uncooked fideua rice and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the white wine vinegar and stir to combine.",
    "Cook, covered, for 5 minutes, or until the rice is tender and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Fluff the fideua with a fork and serve hot."
